abstract: ToTok, an Emirati messaging app that has been downloaded to millions of phones, is the latest escalation of a digital arms race.
snippet: ToTok, an Emirati messaging app that has been downloaded to millions of phones, is the latest escalation of a digital arms race.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — It is billed as an easy and secure way to chat by video or text message with friends and family, even in a country that has restricted popular messaging services like WhatsApp and Skype.
